Package: metabias
Type: Package
Title: Meta-analysis for within-study and/or across-study biases
Description: Provides common components (classes, methods, documentation) for
  packages that conduct meta-analytic corrections and sensitivity analyses
  for within-study and/or across-study biases in meta-analysis. See the packages
  `PublicationBias`, `phacking`, and `multibiasmeta`.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
  person("Mika", "Braginsky", email = "mika.br@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Maya", "Mathur", email = "mmathur@stanford.edu", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Mika Braginsky <mika.br@gmail.com>
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/mikabr/metabias
BugReports: https://github.com/mikabr/metabias/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
